 Pack: 88 Assets</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793480/extras/0c32a1d978471d69821c45705c400b66.avif?t=1694751714\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Underwater Pack: 121 Assets</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793480/extras/43e2ee4327b3b3babfea7291f1b4b0e2.avif?t=1694751714\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><strong>Total DLC Assets So Far: 782</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Free Edition:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Are not able to host their own multiplayer games. They must instead join the lobby of someone who owns the Game Master Edition.<br></li><li> Are only given one save slot for single-player maps. </li></ul>",
